# Problem 2

## Problem 2.1
$\sqrt{x}$ must lie between $x/a$ and $a$ because $x$ divided by its square root should be its square root, or approximately $x/a$.

## Problem 2.2
```julia
function newtons_method(x, a, error) 
  while abs(x/a - a) > error
    x = x/a
    a = (x/a + a)/2
  end
  return a
end
```

